The @UN-led #COVAX initiative has signed an advance purchase agreement with #PfizerBioNTech for up to 40 million doses of its #COVID19 #vaccine. According to the #WHO's @DrTedros, "COVAX is on track to deliver 2 billion doses by the end of this year."
